<h1>Box</h1>
<p>Primary content container used for drawing attention.</p>
<h2 id="demo">Demo</h2>
<code-sample>
<m-box ord="primary">Primary content</m-box>
<m-box ord="secondary">Secondary content. Neighboring Boxes have spacing.</m-box>
<p>Anything outside of a Box is considered tertiary content.</p>
</code-sample>
